以色列外长科恩通电话，反映中国怎样立场？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据外交部网站消息，4 月 17 日，中国国务委员兼外长秦刚分别同巴勒斯坦外长马立基和以色列外长科恩通电话。马立基表示，高度赞赏中方在巴勒斯坦问题上的明确立场，感谢中方支持巴勒斯坦民族自决并独立建国，欢迎中方所做的一切努力。科恩表示，感谢中方愿为解决以巴冲突提供支持。一天之内，秦刚分别与巴以两国外长通话！"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "254 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596250111"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqqrV79fDzJ1AEAMaCDk0NzgxMjAzIO3q96EGMAA4oQJAA3IJNTk2MjUwMTExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1681895289.2640212", "card_id": "Q_583189965", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 224}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "什么方法可以挑出铝粉中的铁粉？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "铝粉中混入了铁粉，而且铝粉经过了某些处理后表面带弱磁性，这种情况下，怎么最大程度挑出铁粉？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-528907835d76d2163d57af3edfa23889_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "203 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/583189965"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqqrV79fDzJ1AEAMaCDkxODc5MzIyIIaHmJ8GMAo4iAJABHIJNTgzMTg5OTY1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1681895289.264958", "card_id": "Q_596338889", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 76}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "马斯克回应特斯拉上海工厂被曝克扣员工绩效，称已知晓将调查，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，特斯拉上海工厂有员工发帖称工厂计划消减员工绩效奖金，4 月 17 日，特斯拉 CEO 埃隆马斯克在推特回应称，已经注意到此事，将进行调查。特斯拉上海工厂被爆克扣员工绩效？马斯克：已知晓，将调查 - 经济观察网 － 专业财经新闻网站"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0ffe882b1a556e233eb32fc06dd53308_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "178 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596338889"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqqrV79fDzJ1AEAMaCDk0ODAwODkyIKTI+aEGMAk4oAFABXIJNTk2MzM4ODg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1681895289.2657278", "card_id": "Q_596459474", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国裁员潮从科技业蔓延至金融、消费业，安永将裁员 3000 人，此前毕马威裁员近 2%，如何看待此事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今年以来，Meta 、谷歌、微软等科技巨头均抛出裁员计划，如今，裁员潮已经从科技业蔓延至金融、消费行业。 近日，「四大」之一的安永宣布计划在美国裁员约 3000 人，以消除「人员过剩」。 除了安永外，毕马威此前也宣布将在美国裁员近 2%，以应对咨询业务大幅放缓的情况，这也成为四大会计师事务所中首家以系统性裁员来应对经济疲软的公司。 截至目前，德勤和普华永道暂无大规模裁员的消息。又一知名巨头宣布：3000 人大裁员！ | 每经网继微软之后，谷歌母公司 Alphabet 宣布裁员 1.2 万人，如何看待美国大型科技公司此番裁员潮？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-846796292321070a490a15135446ea16_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "153 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596459474"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IqqrV79fDzJ1AEAMaCDk0ODI3NjE5IJSA/aEGMAU4dkAGcgk1OTY0NTk0NzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1681895289.2665787", "card_id": "Q_596287317", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 459}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "劳斯莱斯旗下首款纯电动车闪灵在上海车展期间正式亮相，起售价为 575 万元，该车有哪些设计亮点？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "【劳斯莱斯